{
  "stem": "10272.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's what the officer told us, walking in with all-- everything he has on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we are waiting for these three guys to come out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It took about 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And these-- when-- when three-- these three characters came out, we didn't recognize them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were so badly beaten.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were dressed in-- in such a dirty and-- and-- and torn [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] pants.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he had a jacket without-- without a shirt, shoes without laces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the other guy couldn't even put on the shoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The shoes were smaller with-- with one size.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He couldn't put them on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had to come barefoot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was bleeding from the nose from-- the eyes were swollen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he hardly could walk and talk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As they came to us, and we were going to see what happened, they dropped on the floor-- on the street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now the officer didn't know what to do, our crew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To send more through?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He just couldn't believe it what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but all of a sudden, one-- we had a guy who was our-- not-- he was not in charge, but he was our leader.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We recognized him as a leader.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his name was-- was [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Pishto, ?] big guy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We called him the big guy, [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Poli. ?] [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Poli. ?] That was the big guy in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, we are going in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he first told us we drop everything on the street, what we have.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] All-- all the valuables we had to throw away on the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only thing which-- which I left for myself was the-- the postcard which I kept-- [SOBBING] I kept in my hand, my fist.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did not throw away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I kept my shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
